QuickFit Journey Map

Stage | User Action | Pain Points | Solution
Awareness | Discovers QuickFit via social media | Overwhelmed by too many fitness apps | Clear, concise app description, easy signup
Onboarding | Signs up and sets fitness goals | Confusing app setup | Guided onboarding tutorial
Workout | Follows a 10-minute video workout | Short on motivation | Push notifications, gamification, rewards
Tracking | Checks weekly progress | Hard to see improvement | Simple progress dashboard, visual graphs
Retention | Sets new goals | Routine becomes monotonous | Personalized workout suggestions, reminders